# Use Yarn, not npm

This project uses Yarn as its package manager. Never use `npm` commands.

- `yarn` or `yarn install` — install dependencies
- `yarn add <pkg>` — add a dependency
- `yarn add -D <pkg>` — add a dev dependency
- `yarn remove <pkg>` — remove a dependency
- `yarn <script>` — run a package.json script
